// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
//
// The Arista Portal APIs provide CloudVision with programmatic access to resources
// available on the arista.com site.
//
// Resources include:
//      * AlertBase updates (AlertBase.json) and
//      * device software downloads.
//
// APIToken & APITokenConfig are the resource API models which facilitate users to set,
// delete and check the presence of a valid Arista Portal API token.
//
// On-premises deployments may require a proxy to allow reachability between CloudVision
// and arista.com depending on the deployment environment. APIProxy & APIProxyConfig are the
// resource API models which can be used to configure CloudVision with a proxy URL where relevant.
//
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

